asset.hookText: Michael Sieben and company are back with another season from the strange and hilarious world of Camp Ramp. In the season 2 premiere Michael comes face to face with his hoarding addiction, a conspiracy-theorist junk-pile, hallucinogenic cave gas, Will Oldham as a wise prophet, and 'Skate Breaks' with Mark Appleyard and Louie Lopez.
